  "title": "Design Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p>We are seeking a highly creative and experienced <strong>Design Manager</strong> to join our dynamic team. The ideal candidate will possess exceptional design skills and have a strong portfolio demonstrating expertise in various design disciplines. This role will involve leading design projects, collaborating with cross-functional teams, and mentoring junior designers to achieve outstanding visual solutions.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead the design team in creating innovative and bespoke designs that align with client requirements.</li>\n  <li>Oversee all stages of the design process, from initial concept development to project completion.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate closely with clients to understand their vision, preferences, and budget.</li>\n  <li>Ensure the highest quality of design output, maintaining our standard of zero compromises on quality.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with project managers, contractors, and other stakeholders to ensure seamless project execution.</li>\n  <li>Stay updated on industry trends, materials, and new technologies.</li>\n  <li>Mentor and guide junior designers, fostering a collaborative and creative work environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proven experience as a Lead Designer or Design Manager, preferably within the design and construction industry.</li>\n  <li>Strong portfolio showcasing innovative and high-quality design projects.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and client management skills.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in design software (e.g., AutoCAD, SketchUp, Adobe Creative Suite).</li>\n  <li>Strong leadership and team management abilities.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work under pressure and meet tight deadlines.</li>\n  <li>Relevant qualifications in Interior Design, Architecture, or a related field.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive salary and performance-based incentives.</li>\n  <li>Opportunities for professional development and career advancement.</li>\n  <li>Collaborative and supportive work environment.</li>\n</ul>",
